  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world full of monsters, fight terrifying monsters and monster bosses, challenge your way to new lands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strengthen your heroes by developing skills, choose a class to join the battle against monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful and survive as long as you can in this desolate battlefield, fight until you defeat the boss in each area to enter the next new land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feature</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Legendary Heroes Survivals is a top-down platform roguelite game with a 2D solo battle mode where you fight against a large number of invading monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.webm?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.mp4?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Survive the challenges in each level to defeat the boss in each level, collect coins to develop your own character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock new characters, 1 star and 2 star levels (must unlock 1 star before it will show) total 15 characters to challenge higher levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/b3d741a6d13f4f30e2443dab01436ad2.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/b3d741a6d13f4f30e2443dab01436ad2.webm?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/b3d741a6d13f4f30e2443dab01436ad2.mp4?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Develop and upgrade various abilities, totaling more than 10 types, to help our characters become even more capable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/0ea95444e50847d14630b432c9a8aaa7.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/0ea95444e50847d14630b432c9a8aaa7.webm?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/0ea95444e50847d14630b432c9a8aaa7.mp4?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Use special skills unique to each character to fight for survival in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Challenge boss level monsters with unique abilities in each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/736cf674fb460f3a68f9bb25278038e2.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/736cf674fb460f3a68f9bb25278038e2.webm?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/736cf674fb460f3a68f9bb25278038e2.mp4?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world full of monsters, fight terrifying monsters and monster bosses, challenge your way to new lands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strengthen your heroes by developing skills, choose a class to join the battle against monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful and survive as long as you can in this desolate battlefield, fight until you defeat the boss in each area to enter the next new land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feature</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Legendary Heroes Survivals is a top-down platform roguelite game with a 2D solo battle mode where you fight against a large number of invading monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.webm?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/d11da9c97988d486b6a0c62b6b0b6f23.mp4?t=1759772450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Survive the challenges in each level to defeat the boss in each level, collect coins to develop your own character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Unlock new characters, 1 star and 2 star levels (must unlock 1 star before it will show) total 15 characters to challenge higher levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3566580/extras/b3d741a6d13f4f30e2443dab01436ad2.poster.avif?t=1759772450\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\